reviews.text:
Super-duper delicious!
They got yummy and reasonably priced lunch-sets.
Great service , great food
food is quite good.  high end local sushi shop.
Good service, the freshness of food is ok. Moreover, the taste is yummy!

Our experience with Sen-ryo didn't start off very well. My friend went to get a number in the queue, and they said they would call us when our table was ready. So we went to sit at the Coffee Academics around the corner to wait and catch up. Over an hour goes by and no phone call. My friend then goes to check and they said our number had already been called. FAIL. 

They sat us because now it's near the end of lunch rush and they had tables. The servers here felt like they didn't care about us at all, no greetings, smiles, or attentiveness. The only redeeming bit about eating at Sen-Ryo is their food. I ordered their sashimi bowl set, which came with a small salad and miso soup. All of the food was fresh and tasty.

reviews.text:
味道尚可，只是招呼水準欠佳!
年初三晚8時左右，只有數客人等位。帶位的很有趣，回答下輪的客時會問:吧枱坐嗎?人家搖頭，她回應哪要等一等。我自作聰明心想極可能是卡位!越走越遠!有五個空位，她偏帶我們坐最近弄東西的位置! 我就未朋友說怎樣從不問我們是否願意坐吧枱。這會她可精靈了，不扮傻了，立即回應:你願意和人share 枱。我懶得理她!
店員友善，食物有水準，有質素

html_attributions: มณีรัตน์ จ้นเทพหฤทัย

reviews.text:
The mall is grand as well as position as high-end products/services.
There are so many eye-catching display for you to take photos.
You can have a good harbor view here.

This mall has multiple levels. The bottom level has kids clothings and kids stores. The 1st level has couture stores jewelry stores. And all the stores seem to be open to almost 10 o'clock at night which is a really cool thing. It has lots  high end fashion stores for a men women and children all separate.

Huge and very fresh shopping mall in Tsim Sha Tsui, with tons of food and shopping options. This ranges from standard to luxury fare, with plenty of hotels even connecting directly to the complex. Nearby is also the Kowloon side ferry terminal, so this is a great connection point to China and Macau too. If you're in or through TST, chances are visiting here can make your time better.
Very big shopping mall with all the main brands here. Also restaurants. Good for big shopping days.
A huge mall and also a ship dock that accommodates cruise ships. Mall's viewing deck has an amazing view of the HK skyline. A very busy and crowded mall.
